# Keep Godot Asset Library installs limited to the addon itself.
#
# The Asset Library (and GitHub "Download ZIP" / release source archives) use
# `git archive`, which honors `export-ignore`. The files below are only useful
# for developing or demoing this repository -- shipping them to projects that
# install the addon would be noise, and `project.godot` would clash with the
# consumer's own project. Everything under addons/ plus README/LICENSE remains.

/demo/          export-ignore
/.github/       export-ignore
/.gitignore     export-ignore
/.gitattributes export-ignore
/project.godot  export-ignore
/icon.svg       export-ignore
